title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 34700
description:
300 More CDG+MP3 Classic Karaoke Songs for U.   Thank you for helping me seed this mammoth collection over the past 2 months or more.   Once we get to the letter M we will be back to where I left off on Part 22000 where I skipped to the letter M.

Due to changes in the collection since then I have decided that I will re post those files again as many did not have Karaoke Label information but now do as I make my way through last years collection upgrading it with this information and of course re ripping a lot of the material at higher audio bit rates as I go
